Hey!

Simple Camera is an open source Android camera application and is based off Open Camera. 
We have made various changes and redesigned the app. We gave it a more personal theme and improved speed and performance.

Simple Camera v 8.1 is avaliable to download at this time.

Our Open Source apps are posted at 1 version behind current one to prevent bugs, ext.

Please visit http://obvisity.com/donate.html to donate today!

